org.ietf.nea.pa.attribute

Interface PaAttributeValueStringVersionBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ImAttributeValueBuilder, TransmissionObjectBuilder<ImAttributeValue>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PaAttributeValueStringVersionBuilderIetf

    public interface PaAttributeValueStringVersionBuilder
extends ImAttributeValueBuilder
    Generic builder to build an integrity measurement string version attribute value compliant to RFC 5792. It can be used in a fluent way.
